==== In order to compile in the correct way xorg-xserver driver we must do the following  ====

==== Steps ====                                                                                                                                                                           
1) in the file called (config.yml) we must to set the following keys
        unser 'specific_commit' key
                set xserver / xf86-video-intel / xf86-video-vesa / xf86-video-fbdev / xf86-input-evdev 
1.2) to complete the above step, see the folder (latestknowncommits.d) in order to know the commit for each driver

==== Considerations ====
The following driver will not compile with latest commit
- xf86-video-fbdev 
